白，用佢嘅方式愛你係一個而家嘅結果而唔係一個誘因，而｢用你的方式｣去愛你係你期望達到的另一個結果，仍然都未係一個誘因。<br />\n<br />\n如果你的外在(靚/身型) /內在(內涵/談吐) 條件，或者所做的事/性，整個 package 吸引到佢帶給佢滿足感，佢會愛你。這是佢愛你的吸引力，而不會調節佢套價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n佢為左維繫/獨佔你給佢的滿足感，佢願意付出做滿足到你的事 (包括調節價值觀) ，這是佢肯付出的愛。<br />\n<br />\n所以，你要佢肯改變，你要知你自己滿足到佢 d咩，到佢表現不好，就要收起這份滿足感，等佢知唔改變係有一個不良後果的，至有誘因促使佢改變吧？"},{"pid":"8330d5c0a697c5ad36d5cbd240a56e4d20376595","tid":1597064,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e2812bf37233162fd68476b540b63bfaabda0e5","tid":1597064,"uid":71832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99b788a21b2fd6297346d96c6b67b2a542ff24b","tid":1597064,"uid":71832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d406b454f800b15705d542d270cd463c25dd79d4","tid":1597064,"uid":105055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T20:58:42.000Z","msg":"遇到咩事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T20:59:18.000Z","msg":"被帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T21:00:49.000Z","msg":"唔明點解依家啲女咁開放，明知個男嘅有女朋友都要癡埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T23:43:25.000Z","msg":"個男的好正，正到一係心思思想試一次，一係自覺會得到勝利。"},{"pid":"189a9a07445e7e97334331bacea346e805a8ca63","tid":1597064,"uid":71832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8330d5c0a697c5ad36d5cbd240a56e4d20376595","tid":1597064,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e2812bf37233162fd68476b540b63bfaabda0e5","tid":1597064,"uid":71832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99b788a21b2fd6297346d96c6b67b2a542ff24b","tid":1597064,"uid":71832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T20:59:18.000Z","msg":"被帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci